\v 11 \x - \xo 1:11 \xt 2Kin…° 24:14-15, 2Kron 36:10, Jer 27:20\x*Josaea in tata s…ôv…ôi Jekonaea m…®ne pi…ôvni me. Ia n…ôp…®n n…ôha k…®n…ôrhi irapw n…ôkur Isrel h…ôier mh…ôuv…ôn ia t…ôn…ô Papilon.
